      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THORKILDSEN (3) resumed in a Grade 4/5 at Sale and finished fifth over 435m (24.94). Form at the trip sound including three wins. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Has ability and is a key runner. BE A SHADOW (8) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 4.5 lengths at Sale in a handy 24.61. Draws out wide but has the ability and in winning form. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Should be in this for a long way. PAW WALDO (4) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only 1.3 lengths from Daring Bandit in second (19.49) at this track. The form out of last race has been strong. Expected to feature. KARACHI (2) is a last-start placegetter at this track and distance - solid claims again.",
